{
  "stem": "3933.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That would be a historical fact.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said, [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Eric, ?] it's two eventualities.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Or I'm lying to you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Or I'm absolutely made up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Or perhaps, I'm just stupid, and I don't know what I'm reading.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Boy, was I lucky to find in the library the book.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was so lucky when he was here because not always you find what you want.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I find the book, and I brought the thing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he was sitting in this chair, reading, and reading, and reading.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I said, you are going to apologize to me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He couldn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I personally felt it in every way.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Every-- every way.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I got some friends.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Shiksas, a gentile girlfriend, which is very unusual.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was a little bit involved with-- my Polish was immaculate because they make fun of your accent.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My Polish was without accent.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I didn't look Jewish, and I-- I was kind of, a little bit, assimilated with Polish.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But they-- and then I've got some nice boy-- not a boyfriend, a friend, a male friend.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he would say, [SPEAKING POLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know what that means?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The hell.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[POLISH] is the hell.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Almost like, go jump in the lake with-- with-- with male Jews, and little female Jews with us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Kind of compliment for the girl-- for the Jewish girls.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were-- then, like I said-- any-- always-- and then is another thing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Jewish Passover-- they need the blood for the matzos, gentile blood.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You wouldn't believe it, how very primitive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They will-- even the child wouldn't come so fast from school, from kindergarten, or child would walk out, and oh, oh!",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My neighbor next door.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was a little girl, [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Danusha. ?] Her name was [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Danusha. ?] This was all later.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
